- Revamped UI to TradingView-style layout with charts on left, filter results on right
- Added comprehensive stock analysis filter interface with quick scenario buttons and advanced filtering options  
- Integrated http://localhost:8000/api/stocks/scan API with Next.js proxy for CORS handling
- Fixed API calls to match actual API documentation structure with proper scenario parameters
- Refactored "watchlist" to be a simple "Filter Results" display area that shows current filter results directly
- Fixed scenario API calls to only send scenario and limit parameters (e.g., Perfect Momentum only sends scenario=perfect_momentum&limit=20)
- Added default Perfect Momentum API call on app load for immediate stock results
- Simplified logic by removing complex watchlist API calls and just displaying filtered stocks directly
- Enhanced stock cards with better formatting showing price, RSI, momentum score, drawdown, and volume ratio